{"tid":1050500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［彭博評論］美國巨大貿易赤字 反映‘America Is Doing Great’","createTime":"2019-03-07T02:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T00:59:07.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f863b990ae013fc012759abbd78670fc5daf5783","tid":1050500,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:41:05.000Z","msg":"大意：<br />\n- 美國經濟增增長勁，人民買多咗野<br />\n反之外國經濟差 啲人少買野<br />\n所以做成大逆差<br />\n<br />\n- 啲人投資美國股市，買美元<br />\n令美元強勢<br />\n令貿易逆差擴大<br />\n<br />\nTrump&rsquo;s Huge Trade Deficit Means America Is Doing Great<br />\n<br />\nIt's a sign of economic strength when consumers snap up imports.⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2019-03-06/trump-s-huge-trade-deficit-means-america-is-doing-great\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fopinion%2Farticles%2F2019-03-06%2Ftrump-s-huge-trade-deficit-means-america-is-doing-great&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=34b832cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2019-03-06/trump-s-huge-trade-deficit-means-america-is-doing-great</a>"},{"pid":"2347d00f356f1484278af2aaab0c734760450ed5","tid":1050500,"uid":70357,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:42:29.000Z","msg":"咁咪點都贏?"},{"pid":"415ba623ca91775db7734bf6546f76854b5ddec8","tid":1050500,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:48:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得彭博立場，好似親共咁。"},{"pid":"42ef4271889e9b78f5558778731f22a1fb449294","tid":1050500,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2347d00f356f1484278af2aaab0c734760450ed5","tid":1050500,"uid":70357,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:42:29.000Z","msg":"咁咪點都贏?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:26:00.000Z","msg":"分別在於小贏同大贏"},{"pid":"67335046031abd989d5a9fbb438991af29f160c0","tid":1050500,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c32ae28be950c1da8a90a2c8add81c9947ec8c3","tid":1050500,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"415ba623ca91775db7734bf6546f76854b5ddec8","tid":1050500,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:48:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得彭博立場，好似親共咁。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:44:34.000Z","msg":"親共上次就唔會老作話咩晶片 大陸有撚咁撚高級咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個國家淨係識偷搶, 你見連一個 OS 都寫唔撚到.<br />\n<br />\n家下 D 人已經好唔撚妥當奴因為佢贏太多同好多政績.  最大問題當奴只係用貿易不平衡做借口隊冧中共呢隻怪物 (獨裁, 有科技, 有奴民 .. )<br />\n<br />\n美國係世界貨幣所以佢入超係非常正常.  好多傻仔真係當美國好撚需要中國買你 D 貨.  美國根本唔洗靠外貿已經可以頂到個國家 (真正既世界貨幣局 + 印鈔)<br />\n<br />\n佢地講既亦都無錯, 美國有既係錢可以將世界各地既資源用自己印既錢買入.  呢個世界就係咁唔公平, 因為你地個個都信美金.  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d344a0ee2c077b35658021710c32c7769ad1a0","tid":1050500,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T00:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}